  <entry>
    <title>一些你看了肯定会笑的笑话，缓解你的不开心</title>
    <link href="https://blog.keepdai.cn/xiaohua.html"/>
    <id>https://blog.keepdai.cn/xiaohua.html</id>
    <published>2021-01-13T23:52:11.000Z</published>
    <updated>2021-01-14T00:49:21.726Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<blockquote><p>出售奥特曼皮，都是我刚打死的</p></blockquote><p><img src= "https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Daibi-mua/jsdelivr@1.3/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Daibi-mua/jsdelivr@1.3/aoteman.jpg"></p><blockquote><p>从小就相信光，结果打了20多年光棍</p></blockquote><p><img src= "https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Daibi-mua/jsdelivr@1.3/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Daibi-mua/jsdelivr@1.3/guanggun.jpg"></p><blockquote><p>什么舔狗？姐姐说了，我是她的犬系男友</p></blockquote><p><img src= "https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Daibi-mua/jsdelivr@1.3/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Daibi-mua/jsdelivr@1.3/gou.jpg"></p><blockquote><p>别人刷热搜：了解热点，跟热点做爆款，吸引流量，流量变现，财务自由</p><p>我刷热搜：“卧槽！”“啊啊啊啊！”“哈哈哈哈哈哈”</p></blockquote><p><img src= "https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Daibi-mua/jsdelivr@1.3/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Daibi-mua/jsdelivr@1.3/resou.jpg"></p><blockquote><p>以前是我无知，经常不回你的消息，你刚刚发自拍我看到了，我们能重新开始吗？你喜欢什么颜色的癞蛤蟆，我可以自己染</p></blockquote><p><img src= "https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Daibi-mua/jsdelivr@1.3/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Daibi-mua/jsdelivr@1.3/gua.jpg"></p><blockquote><p>小时候偷吃了一板布洛芬，被我妈发现了狂打我，笑死，根本不痛。</p></blockquote><p><img src= "https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Daibi-mua/jsdelivr@1.3/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Daibi-mua/jsdelivr@1.3/v2-58d932e5f63d7876d7676ac3c4f5cea5_hd.jpg"></p><blockquote><p>为什么隔夜水不能喝，早上的水下午却能喝，不都是八个小时吗？也许是因为夜晚有一种毒，我知道了，是孤独。</p></blockquote><p><img src= "https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Daibi-mua/jsdelivr@1.3/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Daibi-mua/jsdelivr@1.3/xiong.jpg"></p><blockquote><p>下雨没带伞 我抬头讲了我的情感经历 老天爷顿时无雨</p></blockquote><p><img src= "https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Daibi-mua/jsdelivr@1.3/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Daibi-mua/jsdelivr@1.3/v2-00519fefd9a1f8501a7e6f16a6a9002b_hd.jpg"></p><blockquote><p>有付出就有回报，你给我100，我给你80，算起来你才付出了20，却得到了80。</p></blockquote><p><img src= "https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Daibi-mua/jsdelivr@1.3/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Daibi-mua/jsdelivr@1.3/v2-ad345eaaa8e28eae4331d2f2a0ac9e2b_hd.jpg"></p><blockquote><p>在超市，我把手伸到条形扫描器上，只见屏幕显示猪蹄8元，我以为机器坏了把脸凑过去看屏幕，显示猪头肉15元。</p></blockquote><p><img src= "https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Daibi-mua/jsdelivr@1.3/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Daibi-mua/jsdelivr@1.3/v2-9a36a60c18f40ad2edd3d78b11e2c464_hd.jpg"></p><blockquote><p>双十一本来想买一套羽绒服，但是仔细一想999感冒灵才二十多块。 </p></blockquote><p><img src= "https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Daibi-mua/jsdelivr@1.3/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Daibi-mua/jsdelivr@1.3/v2-aae107175055a375b6c65c9ae3398d6d_hd.jpg"></p><blockquote><p>去医院检查，医生一边写一边问：喝酒不？ 我一脸懵逼试探性的问：今晚吗？</p></blockquote><p><img src= "https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Daibi-mua/jsdelivr@1.3/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Daibi-mua/jsdelivr@1.3/v2-834bb46add39138197e3d76025738bad_hd.jpg"></p><blockquote><p>不会接吻？那我教你好了 伸出舌头写三遍“abcd”</p></blockquote><p><img src= "https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Daibi-mua/jsdelivr@1.3/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Daibi-mua/jsdelivr@1.3/v2-4759920aac1d107a06019934319823ea_hd.jpg"></p><blockquote><p>刚刚用舌头对着空气划abcd的憨憨有吗？</p></blockquote><p><img src= "https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Daibi-mua/jsdelivr@1.3/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Daibi-mua/jsdelivr@1.3/v2-ba1d0dc209a645ba49b138a99915dde4_hd.jpg"></p><blockquote><p>每次遇到乞丐，他们都向我抖一下碗里的钱，难道这就是炫耀吗？</p></blockquote><p><img src= "https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Daibi-mua/jsdelivr@1.3/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Daibi-mua/jsdelivr@1.3/zhuzhu.jpg"></p><blockquote><p>禁止导盲犬进入是给人看的还是给导盲犬看的？</p></blockquote><p><img src= "https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Daibi-mua/jsdelivr@1.3/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Daibi-mua/jsdelivr@1.3/v2-2510b68d82f4356e89c5322600eb4716_hd.jpg"></p><blockquote><p>我一拳把自己打死了，是强壮还算虚弱？</p></blockquote><p><img src= "https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Daibi-mua/jsdelivr@1.3/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Daibi-mua/jsdelivr@1.3/v2-47e739f4cb56318d9b40eac365ac92ac_hd.jpg"></p><blockquote><p>香菇掉厕所里还能叫香菇吗？</p></blockquote><p><img src= "https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Daibi-mua/jsdelivr@1.3/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Daibi-mua/jsdelivr@1.3/v2-97cb86901136ed73ca59625205e79814_hd.jpg"></p><blockquote><p>没有生育能力这个病会遗传吗？</p></blockquote><p><img src= "https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Daibi-mua/jsdelivr@1.3/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Daibi-mua/jsdelivr@1.3/v2-ad2817fbea2add09b9fcaaf0c8d67c6b_hd.jpg"></p><blockquote><p>陨石为什么能精准地砸进陨石坑里</p></blockquote><p><img src= "https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Daibi-mua/jsdelivr@1.3/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Daibi-mua/jsdelivr@1.3/v2-8022e43c2b6f4aa48366db29f9e7aac9_r.jpg"></p><blockquote><p>一直有个问题轮椅为什么要用手推轮子，改用脚蹬不是更方便吗？</p></blockquote><p><img src= "https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Daibi-mua/jsdelivr@1.3/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Daibi-mua/jsdelivr@1.3/v2-eeb76eb1fb66362d7d520a591f718730_hd.jpg"></p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
